'''Wormtongue''' is a one-man [[:Category:Black metal|Black Metal]] [[Bands|band]] from [[wikipedia:Virginia|Virginia, United States]]. Its sole member is Nate "Hastoth" Adams. The band's name is derivered from [[Gríma|Wormtongue]], the corrupted advisor of [[Théoden]].
